node.text:
Just when I thought I couldn’t love #TheOffice more, @peacocktv sent me a swag box straight from Dunder Mifflin 🤯

Excuse me while I take my Dundie and watch my favorite episodes streaming exclusively on Peacock

#IAmIntel
